icap.core
Class IcapParser

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Thread
      icap.core.IcapParser
All Implemented Interfaces:
Icap, java.lang.Runnable
Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractService
public abstract class IcapParser
extends java.lang.Thread
implements Icap

ICAP protocol parser.
Determine ICAP request type (OPTIONS/REQMOD/RESPMOD), parse ICAP request and embedded HTTP messages for REQMOD and RESPMOD.

Author:
Mittig
